title: Everyone's Roasting Kendall Jenner for Her Sweaty AF-Looking Latex Turtleneck at the Emmys
text:
From Cosmopolitan

Kendall Jenner and Kim Kardashian hit the 2019 Emmy Awards to present an shiny statue to the best reality TV show, and Kendall's latex turtleneck dress is confusing tons of people on Twitter.

Kendall's floral gown is by Richard Quinn, while Kim wore Vivienne Westwood.

Photo credit: Twitter More

Kendall Jenner and Kim Kardashian showed up at the 2019 Emmys to present the award for Best Reality TV Show, which yes they are very qualified for due to being literal life-long reality stars. Frankly, Keeping Up with the Kardashians was robbed and the Emmy committee's silence is deafening!

Um anyway, Kim kept things super simple, by which I mean she wore a bunch of massive diamond necklaces stacked on top of each other, paired with a black Vivienne Westwood dress. While Kendall wore, ya know, this ol' thing:

And people have T-H-O-U-G-H-T-S. First of all, plenty of folks on Twitter are confused about why Kendall and Kim are even at the Emmys, which seems RUDE considering they're TV stars on the aforementioned pop cultural legend that is Keeping Up with the Kardashians.

first, what the fuck is kendall jenner and kim kardashian doing at the #Emmys ? second, what the fuck is she wearing pic.twitter.com/dvWLKVRN43 — 𝓜𝓪𝓻𝔂 (@barzyhsx) September 22, 2019

Kim and Kendall are presenting the reality tv category 😐. Girl i guess #Emmys — Pippi Loansgotme (@mutual_feelings) September 22, 2019

But mostly everyone is deeply concerned about Kendall's outfit which a) I love, how dare you all, and b) basically consists of a very sweaty-seeming black latex turtleneck with a floral dress casually/inexplicably placed over it. And the internet is best described as confused?

Kendall Jenner combines BDSM latex with a lovely autumn picnic style blanket beautifuly #Emmys#ERedCarpetpic.twitter.com/yp1HQJU7C0 — Matt Demers (@MrHollywoodMD) September 22, 2019

no one:

kendall jenner borrowing the rubber suit from ahs at the emmys: pic.twitter.com/kipgr4aAIi — sierra (@silknstyles) September 23, 2019

What in God’s name is Kendall Jenner wearing? #Emmyspic.twitter.com/89nrjPazGj — Trista McGlamery (@tristamac) September 22, 2019

Kendall Jenner serving Alice in Bondageland with that latex + floral getup #Emmyspic.twitter.com/LxUDdhT8xr — Cooper Jackson (@cooperjackson) September 22, 2019

Fine, I'll admit it's a look. But it's also a LOOK.
